            <title>[FELIX-3896] Null reference are injected with @Bind(optional=false) method on iPOJO components</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FELIX-3896</link>
                <project id="12310100" key="FELIX">Felix</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;There are two components in the attached sample&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;One constructor is failing&lt;br/&gt;
This results in providing &quot;null&quot; reference to the other component which is requiring an instance of the given interface.&lt;br/&gt;
We shouldn&apos;t send &quot;null&quot; reference for a component that requires a valid instance of the component.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
